TEAMS REQUEST NIAGARA SWIMMING, INC. ("NI") HOST MEETS UNDER SANCTION FEES OF $25/DAY. NI RECEIVES 50 CENTS PER SWIM. SOME BOARD MEMBERS ASSOCIATE WITH TEAMS HOSTING MEETS, REQUEST SANCTION VIA NI, RUN THE SWIM MEET THEN VIA THIRD PARTY (OTHER SWIM TEAM) CAN RECEIVE COMPENSATION TO RUN THE MEET.

THE GOVERNING BODY OF NIAGARA SWIMMING IS THE HOUSE OF DELEGATES (HOD). THE HOD MEETS TYPICALLY TWICE A YEAR WITH ITS ANNUAL MEETING NO LATER THAN JUNE 15. DURING INTERVALS BETWEEN MEETINGS OF THE HOD, THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE ACTS FOR NIAGARA SWIMMING, INC. WITH EXCEPTIONS OUTLINED IN THE BYLAWS. THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE IS COMPRISED OF 17 MEMBERS AS OUTLINED IN THE ORGANIZATION BYLAWS.
